{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban MPs & Ministers from using a 'disappearing message' function on work phones",
        "additional_details": "The taxpayer deserves to be able to hold MPs and Ministers accountable for their actions.",
        "background": "In order for complete transparency to the UK taxpayer, and to speed up any possible future police enquiries, all MPs' and Ministers' work phones & other devices should not be allowed to have the 'disappearing messages' feature.",
